>
> Unless you're looking for custom stuff (i.e. Sewfine), TMI is pretty much
> the only supplier of "original style" bus upholstery.  So no matter where
> you buy it (and prices vary greatly), it's likely that you'll get TMI
> upholstery.  Even the custom upholstery suppliers like Sewfine typically
> ship TMI as their entry-level stuff.  But this isn't neccessarily a bad
> thing; I have had no problems with TMi's fit and quality.

